M|3-Ye|**Ex|** "By Dec 31, 2028: $15M rv, $2.25M profit (15%), 85 people, 600 active accounts. Regional leader in 3 metros, two $5M+ pd lines, NPS above 60, leadership team of 6 A-players, Best Places to Work recognition."
M|Ques|tx|The 1-Year Plan makes the 3-Year Picture actionable w/ specific targets for the nx twelve months.
M|1-Ye|tx|```
M|1-Ye|Date|____________ (1 year from today)
M|1-Ye|rv|$____________
M|1-Ye|Prof|$____________ (______%)
M|1-Ye|Goal|
M|1-Ye|tx|1. ________________________________
M|1-Ye|tx|2. ________________________________
M|1-Ye|tx|3. ________________________________
M|1-Ye|tx|4. ________________________________
M|1-Ye|tx|5. ________________________________
