M|1-Ye|tx|Every goal shd be specific and measurable. "Improve mk" is not a goal. "gn 500 qualified leads per month by Q4" is a goal.
M|Ques|tx|Rocks are the 3-7 most important priorities for the nx 90 days. They bridge the gap btw the 1-Year Plan and daily execution.
M|Rock|tx|Rocks shd directly support 1-Year Plan goals. If a rock doesn't connect to a goal, question whether it belongs.
M|Rock|tx|\| 1-Year Goal \| Q1 Rock \| Q2 Rock \|
M|Rock|tx|\|------------\|---------\|---------\|
M|Rock|tx|\| gn 500 leads/month \| Launch new website and SEO st \| Hire cn mk specialist \|
M|Rock|tx|\| Reach $8M rv \| Close 3 enterprise deals \| Launch upsell program for existing accounts \|
M|Rock|tx|\| bd leadership team \| Hire VP of Operations \| Complete 90-day onboarding for all new leaders \|
M|Ques|tx|The Issues List captures everything standing in the way of achieving your vision. It includes problems, ideas, and obstacles at the company level.
M|Ques|tx|**Long-term issues** are st and may take quarters to resolve. **Short-term issues** are tactical and shd be solved in the nx Level 10 meeting.
